30 the preceding state fiscal year; divided by
31 (ii) the total adjusted gross receipts received by licensees
32 from gambling games authorized under this article during
33 the state fiscal year ending June 30, 2020;
34 shall be set aside for revenue sharing under subsection (d).
35 (2) Subject to subsection (c), twenty-five percent (25%) of the
